                  "Binario Nativo"
                ]
              },
              "correctIndex": 1,
              "explanation": {
                "EN": "It targets the Substrate Contracts Pallet which runs a WASM VM.",
                "ES": "Apunta al Pallet de Contratos de Substrate que corre una VM WASM."
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "q-ink-1-2",
              "question": {
                "EN": "What macro defines the contract storage?",
                "ES": "¿Qué macro define el almacenamiento del contrato?"
